('romeo_and_juliet_act2_scene6',15,'Enter Juliet.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act2_scene6',15,'Here comes the lady: O, so light a foot Will ne’er wear out the everlasting flint: A lover may bestride the gossamer That idles in the wanton summer air, And yet not fall; so light is vanity.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act2_scene6',32,'Exeunt.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',0,'Enter Mercutio, Benvolio, Page, and Servants.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',30,'Enter Tybalt and others.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',46,'Enter Romeo.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',64,'Draws.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',71,'Drawing.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',81,'Exit Page.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',94,'Exeunt Mercutio and Benvolio.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',100,'Reenter Benvolio.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',109,'Reenter Tybalt.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',109,'Now, Tybalt, take the villain back again, That late thou gavest me; for Mercutio’s soul Is but a little way above our heads, Staying for thine to keep him company: Either thou, or I, or both, must go with him.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',117,'Exit Romeo.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',117,'Enter Citizens, etc.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',121,'Enter Prince, attended; Montague, Capulet, their Wives, and others.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene1',177,'Exeunt.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene2',0,'Enter Juliet.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene2',33,'Enter Nurse, with cords.'),
('romeo_and_juliet_act3_scene2',33,'Now, nurse, what news? What hast thou there? the cords That Romeo bid thee fetch?'),
